		<p>
			<span>This is AccuPay</span>, an AccuLynx Mobile Payment application for collecting a
			secure online payment at the job location. The application needed to
			include ACH and Credit Card processing that worked seamlessly with the
			desktop application by automatically updating the job information and
			notifying any required users of the completed transaction.
		</p>
