			<strong>Who is Doug Cash?</strong><br/>
      Doug is a Retail Roofing Business owner who needs a way
			to collect payment without waiting for the customer to send a check. The
			ideal workflow was collecting payment on completion of the final
			walk-through at the end of the project.
