		<p>
			What are other applications doing to collect payment promptly? What are
			some roadblocks? What's working for them? What's not?
		</p>
   <h4>A couple of things to note:</h4>
    <li class="bullet"><span>&#10112;</span> There are a lot of card service providers with just a few top providers. </li>
    <li><span>&#10113;</span> It has to be simple and intuitive and feel safe.</li>
    <li><span>&#10114;</span> It won't take much frustration before a user quits.
    </li>
